            </table><br clear="all" /><div id="title"><span style="font-weight:normal;font-size:0.9em;"> An act to amend the Budget Act of 2022 (Chapters 43, 45, and 249 of the Statutes of 2022) by amending Item 3900-101-0001
                  of Section 2.00 of, and amending Sections 19.56 and 39.10 of, that act, to amend the Budget Act of 2023 (Chapters 12, 38,
