                     <tr>
                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24">2.</td>
                        <td colspan="5" valign="top" width="288">
                           <div style="">Of the funds appropriated in Schedule (1), up to $134,413,000 shall be available to provide special education and related
                              services to pupils with low-incidence disabilities pursuant to their individualized education program. The Superintendent
                              of Public Instruction shall allocate these funds to special education local plan areas on an equal per-pupil rate using the
