                           </div>
                        </td>
                        <td valign="bottom" width="80"></td>
                     </tr>
                     <tr>
                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24">3.</td>
                        <td colspan="5" valign="top" width="288">
                           <div style="">Of the funds appropriated in Schedule (1), up to $39,738,000 shall be available for the purposes of vocational training and
                              job placement for special education pupils through Project Workability I pursuant to Article 3
                              					 (commencing with Section 56470) of Chapter 4.5 of Part 30 of Division 4 of Title 2 of the Education Code. As a condition
