                              funds received pursuant to this provision, devoted to the provision of vocational education for special education pupils shall
                              be maintained at or above the level provided in the 1984–85 fiscal year. The Superintendent of Public Instruction may waive
                              this requirement for local educational agencies that demonstrate that the requirement would impose a severe hardship.
                           </div>
                        </td>
                        <td valign="bottom" width="80"></td>
