                     <tr>
                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24">4.</td>
                        <td colspan="5" valign="top" width="288">
                           <div style="">Of the funds appropriated in Schedule (1), up to $162,053,000 is available to fund the costs of children placed in licensed
